Give great service to your customers
Keep your star rating high and cancellation rate low to enjoy Uber Pro rewards.
Your points, ratings, and cancellation rate from Aug 1 - Oct 31 determine your rewards from Nov 1 - Jan 31.

You earn points during fixed 3-month periods. Points reset after each period. 

When you earn enough points to unlock the next level of rewards, you start enjoying your new rewards right away. Give great service to continue enjoying rewards until the end of the next 3-month period.
